# Agent Lookup Rule

- Treat Stream Heaven agents as markdown files, not npm packages.
- For agent discovery, use `ai-agents/AGENT-REGISTRY.md` first.
- For filtered search, use `node scripts/list-agents.mjs` with:
  - `--phase <value>`
  - `--domain <value>`
  - `--search <value>`
- Prefer returning exact agent file paths and `@`-mentionable paths.
- Use `scripts/validate-agents.mjs` to confirm catalog health after bulk updates.

